Description: PHP library to build console style tables
 ConsoleTable makes you easy to build console style tables. It helps you to
 display tabular data in terminal/shell. It supports bordered and non-bordered
 tables, custom padding, indentation, and column alignment.
 .
 This is a component of the PHPLucidFrame framework.
